### Purchase Order API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@companyId = 60f7b1b3e4b0a3a3a3a3a3a3
@vendorId = 60f7b1b3e4b0a3a3a3a3a3a4
@purchaseOrderId = 60f7b1b3e4b0a3a3a3a3a3a5
@authToken = your_jwt_token_here

### Create Purchase Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/finance/purchases/purchase-orders/createPurchaseOrder
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "vendorId": "{{vendorId}}",
  "purchaseOrderNumber": "PO-2025-0001",
  "purchaseOrderDate": "2025-08-02T00:00:00.000Z",
  "expectedDeliveryDate": "2025-08-15T00:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "draft",
  "priority": "medium",
  "taxType": "exclusive",
  "discountType": "flat",
  "discountValue": 100,
  "shipping": 50,
  "roundOff": true,
  "items": [
    {
      "itemId": "60f7b1b3e4b0a3a3a3a3a3a6",
      "name": "Sample Item 1",
      "hsn": "1234",
      "unit": "pcs",
      "quantity": 10,
      "rate": 100,
      "discount": 5,
      "discountType": "flat",
      "taxType": "cgst_sgst",
      "taxRate": 18,
      "cess": [
        {
          "name": "Environment Cess",
          "rate": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Sample Item 2",
      "hsn": "5678",
      "unit": "kg",
      "quantity": 5,
      "rate": 200,
      "discount": 10,
      "discountType": "percentage",
      "taxType": "igst",
      "taxRate": 12
    }
  ],
  "terms": "Payment within 30 days",
  "notes": "Handle with care"
}

###

### Get All Purchase Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/finance/purchases/purchase-orders/getAllPurchaseOrders/{{companyId}}?page=1&limit=10&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Purchase Order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/finance/purchases/purchase-orders/purchaseOrderDetails/{{companyId}}/{{purchaseOrderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Update Purchase Order
PUT {{baseUrl}}/finance/purchases/purchase-orders/updatePurchaseOrderDetails/{{companyId}}/{{purchaseOrderId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "status": "sent",
  "priority": "high",
  "expectedDeliveryDate": "2025-08-20T00:00:00.000Z",
  "notes": "Updated notes - urgent delivery required"
}

###

### Search Purchase Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/finance/purchases/purchase-orders/searchPurchaseOrders/{{companyId}}?q=PO-2025
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Update Approval Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/finance/purchases/purchase-orders/updateApprovalStatus/{{companyId}}/{{purchaseOrderId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "approvalStatus": "approved"
}

###

### Acknowledge by Vendor
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/finance/purchases/purchase-orders/acknowledgeByVendor/{{companyId}}/{{purchaseOrderId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "vendorComments": "Order acknowledged. Will deliver as per schedule."
}

###

### Add Attachment
POST {{baseUrl}}/finance/purchases/purchase-orders/addAttachment/{{companyId}}/{{purchaseOrderId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "url": "https://example.com/attachment.pdf"
}

###

### Remove Attachment
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/finance/purchases/purchase-orders/removeAttachment/{{companyId}}/{{purchaseOrderId}}/0
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Purchase Order Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/finance/purchases/purchase-orders/stats/{{companyId}}?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Bulk Delete Purchase Orders
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/finance/purchases/purchase-orders/bulkDeletePurchaseOrders/{{companyId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "purchaseOrderIds": [
    "{{purchaseOrderId}}",
    "60f7b1b3e4b0a3a3a3a3a3a7"
  ]
}

###

### Delete Purchase Order
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/finance/purchases/purchase-orders/deletePurchaseOrder/{{companyId}}/{{purchaseOrderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
